{"tid":339297,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"超推薦一下大家睇 Phantom 幻靈鎮魂曲, 係講殺手的","createTime":"2017-07-29T02:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T21:28:56.000Z","uid":75100,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a10eaeadbb4d1f940653395d99f2bec2eb4345f8","tid":339297,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/105255_8724a2a062a78542b3e01efc56844084.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F105255_8724a2a062a78542b3e01efc56844084.JPG&h=aead5e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n合共26集，但我用左2日就睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n直到今日，都仲會諗返起d情節而感到有d難受，畢竟係由 虛淵玄 寫劇本架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面想簡單評下+介紹下呢套野，我文筆唔好，或者唔可以將想表達既野清楚打出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>世界觀+劇情介紹</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/105228_20c34dbdc52eedb7c49e5381899b2289.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F105228_20c34dbdc52eedb7c49e5381899b2289.JPG&h=e0dfedd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　吾妻玲二原只是個平凡的日本少年，因來洛杉磯旅行時意外捲入一場暗殺事件，而遭受他人的追殺與囚禁。幸運的是，玲二因天賦異稟受到組織的青睞；不幸的是，他的天賦卻也讓自己陷入黑暗的世界中，成為Inferno的一分子。從此之後，玲二脫胎換骨。他失去過往的記憶、身分、姓名，成為Inferno所培育的殺手，並被賦予新的名字──『Zwei』。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n本作的主要劇情，都會圍繞黑社會為背景，描述男主角作為『Zwei』的暗殺生涯。本來男主角係好唔願意，但慢慢發生左各式各樣既事，慢慢開始迷失自我，變成殺人的機器。從一開始既訓練，後來既暗殺實戰，觀眾會清楚感受到男主角既成長。而做殺手既過程中，亦同好多人發生左唔同程度既愛恨糾葛，導致左好多悲劇，呢點亦都係本作既賣點。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>畫風</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n一般呢種殺手類既，畫風可能一般，但呢套唔同，睇慣萌番既人，一定都可以接受到。我會睇呢套片既原因，有大半係因為望到封面圖中既女主角。我寫包單，男主角同幾個重要既女角色都好鬼正!!!!!! 而且D槍畫得好仔細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/105438_2605b2f266dcc2d34a6be7b3c1c71cb3.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F105438_2605b2f266dcc2d34a6be7b3c1c71cb3.JPG&h=cf3cba9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"10a22b3352a08bde9388c1bfd5755f22f213f792","tid":339297,"uid":121771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"好多年前睇過 結局好 悲傷， 整體 係一套 神作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f36e8e20e5e65f3a5e8758cf32820be18a206b9","tid":339297,"uid":75100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:07:26.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong>劇情短評</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n呢套野，主要可以分為三部分，前中後部。我無咩文筆，驚劇透所以只好寫得淺D<br />\n<br />\n前部，係男主角岩岩被人老粒，然後被人逼佢學做殺手既訓練過程。由拿唔起槍，慢慢百發百中 ; 由唔敢殺人，到第一次殺完人崩潰.......描述既係玲二是如何變成殺手Zwei。 係呢1 part， 男主角同女主角有好多交集，女主角係最強的殺手Phantom，佢已經係一部殺人如麻既機器，但玲二既出現，令女主角既內心出現波動。就算被洗去記憶 ，沒有明天，更沒有未來，但玲二既不屈服，會唔會令女主角改變呢? <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/110122_9bc7a735f2af1cd2882262557470987f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F110122_9bc7a735f2af1cd2882262557470987f.JPG&h=4ffded4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中部 : 因為某個悲劇，男主角崩潰左，開始封閉自己既內心，變成笑住殺人既痴線佬，令人慘不忍睹。但呢個時候，因某件大茶飯，男主角遇到一個可愛幼女，通過同溫柔又天真既幼女一齊生活，男主角開始醒悟，找回了自我，坦然面對自己既內心。但呢一次相遇，又會否帶來另一次悲劇呢? <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/110520_636f1f42131b56fca2f4b45de369e43d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F110520_636f1f42131b56fca2f4b45de369e43d.JPG&h=b4239521&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後部: 唔識講啦屌，講埋唔使睇架啦你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之呢套野對殺手既描述，係十分貼地的，唔會有d咩外掛超能力，最多都係高速瞬移+ 被幾十人圍射都唔會中子彈 之類既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68461b3965d71606e8627d020790fa1971e68ae3","tid":339297,"uid":12289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:11:34.000Z","msg":"睇到嗰post令我諗番起音樂盒首bgm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得最後係咪死淨女主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f56dfbe1ef039c8eb0f2589043c494bceafbab","tid":339297,"uid":75100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:15:30.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>結語</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n愛的戰士係一條食屎狗，佢好鐘意誤導觀眾，你以為會係good end，但下一秒就會變成悲劇，咁既情況係Phantom出現左好多次!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得由情感方面來說，本作塑造的相當成功。故事細膩的描繪出角色之間既生離死別、喜怒哀樂。觀眾都可以幾感同身受........<br />\n<br />\n但呢套野我覺得唔太好既一點，就係無愛情線。無愛情線!!!? 你係咪想話女殺手同男殺手一齊同居，執行任務，應該仲拯救左佢出地獄，居然無互相鐘意大家,，然後啪啪啪咁神奇????<br />\n<br />\n無錯，我唔知gal game入面佢地有無做愛做既事，但係動畫，比起愛情，玲二同Ein既關係，更類似於戰友，親友，大家互相的心靈寄託之所。雖然佢地最後無結婚之類，而且仲有好多峰迴路轉既悲劇，但我衷心覺得Ein可以遇上Zwei ，真係太好了!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/111512_eea411aa3d5ab86b040f57412c629b1c.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F111512_eea411aa3d5ab86b040f57412c629b1c.JPG&h=5a44073a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b356b7d5b1cbaf8d5490f6e369c22987215c936","tid":339297,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:17:33.000Z","msg":"唯一一點我覺得bug既，就係點解區區2年，一個幼女可以變成大波靚女!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/111644_636f1f42131b56fca2f4b45de369e43d.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F111644_636f1f42131b56fca2f4b45de369e43d.JPG&h=31f4eeae&s={SIZE}\" />&gt;<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/29/111650_7e53fa31a2260fa786bfc82f92c8f3cd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F29%2F111650_7e53fa31a2260fa786bfc82f92c8f3cd.JPG&h=83e2ecaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f262eb76f59e5ee59c3ab59a6fb2ac61ab48187","tid":339297,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:29:05.000Z","msg":"個結局咁 所以我冇推過比身邊既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20d60fa7556a33adb0b498a4a8137cd891fe677","tid":339297,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到嗰post令我諗番起音樂盒首bgm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得最後係咪死淨女主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔覺得會放過埋女主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ecacdd8ec4efc9ff6175d6a412c356b4cf38cd2","tid":339297,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:31:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇到嗰post令我諗番起音樂盒首bgm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得最後係咪死淨女主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔覺得會放過埋女主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我覺得2個頂尖殺手，有咩可能察覺唔到殺氣<br />\n<br />\n男主角就應該因為心願了左9成，幫ein返到去，所以甘心被殺，贖罪呢咁多年做過既壞事。女主角就唔知啦.....希望唔好啦"},{"pid":"8607ef5ea18390cfbb1b9f96caffe8be31563a5e","tid":339297,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:36:28.000Z","msg":"好想知卡爾細個沖完涼個幕係咪同主角扑左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896c36012def84bb8b7c9d8481af6dfabcfbed1b","tid":339297,"uid":52112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c